<div id="content" class="backgrnd4"><div id="right"><div id="box6"><h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">Proceedings of the Fifteenth Innovative Applications of Artificial IntelligenceConference</span></h2><div class="content"><p><i>Sponsored by the Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</i></p><p><b>Edited by John Riedl and Randy Hill</b></p><p>August 12&ndash;14, 2003, Acapulco, Mexico. Published by The AAAI Press, Menlo Park, California. <a href="../../Press/Proceedings/iaai03.php">This proceedings is also available in book format.</a></p><p><b>Please Note:</b> Abstracts are linked to individual titles, and will appear in a separate browser window. Full-text versions of the papers are linked to the abstract text. Access to full text may be restricted to AAAI members. PDF file sizes may be large!</p><hr /><h3 class="left">Contents</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-000.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Preface</a> / vii<br /><i>John Riedl and Randall W. Hill</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-022.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">AAAI Orgnization</a> / ix</p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-023.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">IAAI-03 Program Committee</a> / xii</p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-024.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Invited Talks</a> / xiii</p><h3 class="left">Deployed Applications</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-001.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">CriterionSM Online Essay Evaluation: An Application forAutomated Evaluation of Student Essays</a> / 3<br /><i>Jill Burstein, Martin Chodorow, and Claudia Leacock</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-002.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The NASD Securities Observation, New Analysis and Regulation System (SONAR)</a> / 11<br /><i>Henry Goldberg, Dale Kirkland, Dennis Lee, Ping Shyr, and Dipak Thakker</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-003.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Cellular Telephone-Based Application for Skin-Grading to Support Cosmetic Sales</a> / 19<br /><i>Hironori Hiraishi and Fumio Mizoguchi</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-004.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">TPO: A System for Scheduling and Managing Train Crew in Norway</a> / 25<br /><i>Jo&atilde;o P. Martins, Ernesto Morgado, and Rolf Haugen</i></p><h3 class="left">Emerging Applications</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-005.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Building Agents for the Customer Service Front</a> / 35<br /><i>Mihai Barbuceanu, Mark S. Fox, Lei Hong, Yannick Lallement, and Zhongdong Zhang</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-006.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Knowledge Acquisition Tool for Course of Action Analysis</a> / 43<br /><i>Kim Barker, Jim Blythe, Gary Borchardt, Vinay K. Chaudhri, Peter E. Clark, Paul Cohen, Julie Fitzgerald, Ken Forbus, Yolanda Gil, Boris Katz, Jihie Kim, Gary King, Sunil Mishra, Clayton Morrison, Ken Murray, Charley Otstott, Bruce Porter, Robert C. Schrag, Tom&aacute;s Uribe, Jeff Usher, and Peter Z. Yeh</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-007.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Searching for Hidden Messages: Automatic Detection of Steganography</a> / 51<br /><i>George Berg, Ian Davidson, Ming-Yuan Duan, and Goutam Paul</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-008.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Transparent Grid Computing: A Knowledge-Based Approach</a> / 57<br /><i>Jim Blythe, Ewa Deelman, Yolanda Gil, and Carl Kesselman</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-009.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Say Cheese!: Experiences with a Robot Photographer</a> / 65<br /><i>Zachary Byers, Michael Dixon, William D. Smart, and Cindy M. Grimm</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-010.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Infrastructure Components for Large-Scale Information Extraction Systems</a> / 71<br /><i>William W. Cohen</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-011.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Applying Reinforcement Learning to Packet Scheduling in Routers</a> / 79<br /><i>Herman Ferra, Ken Lau, Christopher Leckie, and Anderson Tang</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-012.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Qualitative Spatial Reasoning about Sketch Maps</a> / 85<br /><i>Kenneth D. Forbus, Jeffrey Usher, and Vernell Chapman</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-013.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">TEXTAL&trade;: Artificial Intelligence Techniques for Automated Protein Structure Determination</a> / 93<br /><i>Kreshna Gopal, Reetal Pai, Thomas R. Ioerger, Tod D. Romo, and James C. Sacchettini</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-014.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Guided Conversations about Leadership: Mentoring with Movies and Interactive Characters</a> / 101<br /><i>Randall Hill, Jr., Jay Douglas, Andrew Gordon, Fred Pighin, and Martin van Velsen</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-015.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Teachable Agents: Learning by Teaching Environments for Science Domains</a> / 109<br /><i>Krittaya Leelawong, Karun Viswanath, Joan Davis, Gautam Biswas, Nancy Vye,Kadira Belynne, and John Bransford</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-016.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Broadcast News Understanding and Navigation</a> / 117<br /><i>Mark Maybury</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-017.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Probabilistic Vehicle Diagnostic System Using Multiple Models</a> / 123<br /><i>Matthew L. Schwall, J. Christian Gerdes, Bernard B&auml;ker, and Thomas Forchert</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-018.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Secure Mobile Agents on Ad Hoc Wireless Networks</a> / 129<br /><i>Evan Sultanik, Donovan Artz, Gustave Anderson, Moshe Kam, William Regli, Max Peysakhov, Jonathan Sevy, Nadya Belov, Nicholas Morizio, and Andrew Mroczkowski</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-019.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The Analogical Thesaurus</a> / 137<br /><i>Tony Veale</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-020.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">LAW: A Workbench for Approximate Pattern Matching in Relational Data</a> / 143<br /><i>Michael Wolverton, Pauline Berry, Ian Harrison, John Lowrance, David Morley, Andres Rodriguez, Enrique Ruspini, and Jerome Thomere</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2003/iaai03-021.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Index</a> / 151</p></div></div></div><div id="left">
